{
  "texts": [
    "The network was always trained for one epoch; any further training was found to destabilize validation metrics.",
    "Increasing regularization does not influence validation metrics destabilization.",
    "We studied the influence of self-attention block and sharpness-aware minimization on network performance.",
    "For the former case, the selfattention was removed so that the averaging was performed directly on every spectrum embedding.",
    "This led to a ≈ 3% decrease in the final cross-validated accuracy."
  ]
}